---
const mailto = "mailto:dlpilosof@gmail.com?subject=Comparing%20notes%20on%20AI%20in%20finance";
---
<section id="top" class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex flex-col justify-center px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 py-24 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-4xl">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-text-muted mb-7">
      Tel Aviv · 4 languages
    </p>

    <h1 class="text-display font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.05] mb-6">
      Diego Pilosof.
    </h1>

    <p class="text-h2 font-semibold text-text-dim mb-2 tracking-tight">
      Strategic Finance <span class="text-accent">&</span> FP&A.
    </p>

    <p class="text-lead text-text-dim max-w-2xl mb-8 leading-relaxed">
      Building AI workflows for finance and revenue operations.
    </p>

    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-light font-semibold leading-snug max-w-3xl mb-7">
      Finance people who read API docs and engineers who understand revenue recognition rarely live in the same person.
      <span class="text-accent">I work in that gap.</span>
    </p>

    <p class="text-text-dim text-base mb-3 max-w-2xl">
      Most recently: Financial Controller at Compugen, a Nasdaq-listed technology company.
    </p>

    <p class="font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-muted tracking-wide mb-10">
      CPA · Big 4 trained · MERN engineer
    </p>

    <p class="text-text-dim text-sm md:text-base mb-5 max-w-2xl">
      If you lead a finance function and you're putting AI in your stack, let's compare notes.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
      <a
        href={mailto}
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent text-primary px-5 py-3 font-mono text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide hover:bg-accent-2 transition-colors group"
      >
        Email me
        <span class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5">→</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/cv/Diego_Pilosof_CV.pdf"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-text-muted/40 text-text-light px-5 py-3 font-mono text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-colors"
        download
      >
        Download CV
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a
    href="#about"
    class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 md:left-12 lg:left-24 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-text-muted hover:text-accent transition-colors"
    aria-label="Scroll to About section"
  >
    scroll ↓
  </a>
</section>
